skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: world pop quiz
des: Play an pop quiz with Alexa. We test your knowledge of world population using our popular World Population Data Sheet as a reference. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to leave.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
